OL,3,CShould you switch or fix? Energy bills
OL,4,Cto rise from October
OL,6,FWhat is Ofgem's price cap and why is
OL,7,Fit rising?
OL,9,FThe price cap, which is set by the
OL,10,Fenergy regulator Ofgem, sets a limit
OL,11,Fon the maximum amount suppliers can
OL,12,Fcharge households in England, Scotland
OL,13,Fand Wales for each kilowatt hour (kWh)
OL,14,Fof energy they use.
OL,16,FEnergy is regulated separately in
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland.
