OL,3,CShould you switch or fix? Energy bills
OL,4,Cto rise from October
OL,6,FOfgem's price cap determines the
OL,7,Famount paid by those households on a
OL,8,Fstandard variable tariff. Those on a
OL,9,Ffixed price deal - where the unit
OL,10,Frates and standing charges are fixed
OL,11,Ffor the length of the contract,
OL,12,Fusually a year - are immune.
OL,14,FTherefore, it could be a good time to
OL,15,Fconsider switching to a fixed-priced
OL,16,Fdeal.
