OL,3,CShould you switch or fix? Energy bills
OL,4,Cto rise from October
OL,6,FMost fixed deals are set for at least
OL,7,Fa year, meaning that the rate is
OL,8,Fguaranteed for 12 months. Some
OL,9,Fproviders will charge an early exit
OL,10,Ffee to end these deals, but not all do.
OL,12,FWhen seeking to switch to a fixed
OL,13,Ftariff, a quick search online on a
OL,14,Fcomparison site that lists all
OL,15,Fsuppliers - rather than just those who
OL,16,Fpay the site to advertise their deals
OL,17,F- is recommended.
OL,19,FOfgem's Tim Jarvis urges customers to
OL,20,Fconsider a fixed tariff to avoid being
OL,21,Faffected by the energy price cap rise
