OL,6,FCurrently, eight million customers pay
OL,7,Fby standard credit, but could be
OL,8,Fmaking savings of #135.60 with one
OL,9,Fsimple switch.
OL,11,FWhat other help is available?
OL,13,FAround 2.7 million more low-income
OL,14,Fhouseholds, including 900,000 families
OL,15,Fwith children, are eligible for the
OL,16,F#150 Warm Home Discount this winter.
OL,18,FIt comes after the government U-turned
OL,19,Fon its winter fuel payments, removing
OL,20,Fthe 'hard to heat' eligibility
OL,21,Fcriteria.
